<li dir=3D"ltr" role=3D"presentation">Absolute Error =3D |Experimental Meas=
urement =E2=80=93 Actual Measurement|</li>
<li dir=3D"ltr" role=3D"presentation">Relative Error=3D Absolute Error/Actu=
al Measurement</li>
<li dir=3D"ltr" role=3D"presentation">Percentage Error =3D Decimal Form of =
Relative Error x 100.<br>
<span id=3D"docs-internal-guid-de207b52-7fff-bff0-fbb0-c7ceeac604f2">&nbsp;=
</span></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"ltr" style=3D"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 1=
